These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, iced-tea
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, kale
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
2. the person eating kale is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | sprite |
| Food       | cabbage | kale |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, parkour
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | lemonade |
| Sport      | parkour     | water-polo  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: adventure, drama
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, thai
1. the russian is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the russian is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | drama  |
| Nationality   | russian | thai |

 #################################

 
