.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-8::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, magic-tricks
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, social-worker
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | photography |
| Job     | freelancer        | social-worker |

